                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-190-off1017 t18280410-190-cd1018"></join>, 1 half-crown, 1 shilling, and 2 farthings, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18280410-190-victim1082" type="victimName">
                        James 
                        Squires
                     <interp inst="t18280410-190-victim1082" type="surname" value="Squires"></interp>
